README:
In the behaviour logs the trial types are numeric. The following code was used. 

For session 1 runs:
trial_type: 1=csp shock; 2=csp view; 3=csp imagine; 4=csm view; 5=csm imagine
shock: 1 = on; 2 = off
Orientation: orientation of the gabor being viewed OR imagined

Sub-27 was not included in analyses due to technical issues with shock

3 dummy volumes should be removed at the start of each event file
